  Б                                                                         Б
  Б  A universal in-circuit indirect  programmer  of  parallel  NOR  flash  Б
  Б  memories. Programs flash memories  connected  to  any  JTAG-compliant  Б
  Б  device  by  manipulating  the  device's  pins   using   boundary-scan  Б
  Б  technology.                                                            Б
  Б                                                                         Б
  Б  Indirect programming using boundary-scan                               Б
  Б                                                                         Б
  Б  By utilizing boundary-scan (JTAG) test logic on a chip  connected  to  Б
  Б  flash memory (e.g. CPU, FPGA, CPLD, ASIC), TopJTAG  Flash  Programmer  Б
  Б  'detaches' the chip's core from its pins and manipulates pins signals  Б
  Б  in order to communicate with flash memory.                             Б
  Б                                                                         Б
  Б                                                                         Б
  Б  No dependence on logic inside JTAG IC                                  Б
  Б                                                                         Б
  Б  The chip connected to flash memory could be  any  JTAG-compliant  IC.  Б
  Б  TopJTAG Flash Programmer works independently on any logic inside  the  Б
  Б  JTAG chip. There is no need to load any code  or  firmware  into  the  Б
  Б  JTAG chip.                                                             Б
  Б                                                                         Б
  Б                                                                         Б
  Б  Most of popular parallel NOR flash memories supported                  Б
  Б                                                                         Б
  Б  TopJTAG Flash Programmer can work with any parallel NOR flash  memory  Б
  Б  compatible with AMD or Intel standard or extended command sets.  Both  Б
  Б  CFI (Common Flash Interface) and non-CFI memories are supported.       Б
  Б                                                                         Б
  Б                                                                         Б
  Б  Common programming functions provided                                  Б
  Б                                                                         Б
  Б  Read, erase, blank check, program, verify,  sector  lock/unlock  (for  Б
  Б  Intel memories), get device ID, view  CFI  info,  autodetect  command  Б
  Б  set.                                                                   Б
  Б                                                                         Б
  Б                                                                         Б
  Б  Disadvantage: slow programming                                         Б
  Б                                                                         Б
  Б  In order to put flash memory pins into certain states,  the  software  Б
  Б  needs to shift entire JTAG chain bits (there are usually hundreds  of  Б
  Б  bits to  shift).  This   makes   the   indirect   programming   using  Б
  Б  boundary-scan to be quite slow.                                        Б
  Б                                                                         Б
  Б                                                                         Б
  Б  Many popular JTAG cables supported                                     Б
  Б  - Altera USB-Blaster                                                   Б
  Б  - USB to JTAG interfaces based on FTDI FT2232 chip, e.g.               Б
  Б  - Amontec JTAGkey-2, JTAGkey and JTAGkey-Tiny                          Б
  Б  - Olimex ARM-USB-TINY-H, ARM-USB-OCD and ARM-USB-TINY                  Б
  Б  - SEGGER J-Link                                                        Б
  Б  - Digilent JTAG-USB                                                    Б
  Б  - Xilinx Parallel Cable III and IV                                     Б
  Б  - Altera ByteBlaster MV and II                                         Б
  Б  - Lattice Parallel ispDOWNLOAD                                         Б
  Б  - Wiggler                                                              Б
  Б  - Embest EasyICE                                                       Б
